Package client.loginWindow

Class LoginViewModel

java.lang.Object
client.loginWindow.LoginViewModel
public class LoginViewModel extends Object
Binds the data coming from the LoginModel with its respective GUI-elements and manages the presentation logic for the login window.
Author:
Felicia Saruba, Nargess Ahmadi, Minghao Li
